title: Nigel Sylvester X ASAP Ferg - "S.O.M.P"
description: Nigel Sylvester & ASAP Ferg team up in this new video which showcases both of their talents. Featuring Nigel riding in California, Istanbul & New York to Ferg performing his hit single "Work" at Nigel's S.O.M.P (Standing On My Pedals) event in Long Beach, CA. These two NYC based talents are stars in BMX and music respectively, this only the beginning of more to come as they continue their ascent in their careers.
